<p>And on Sunday, Millie Mackintosh, 31, posed for a smiley snap with baby Sienna, four months, and shared a video of her little girl 'trying to say her first word.' </p>

<p>The former Made In Chelsea star took to Instagram, where she shared the adorable footage of her baby lying in her crib, attempting to say 'hello.'</p>

